      <title>Markdown</title>
      <link href="/other/markdown/"/>
      <url>/other/markdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Markdown 是一种轻量级标记语言，允许使用简单的文本格式来编写具备特定排版格式的文档</p><hr><h2 id="基础语法">基础语法</h2><h3 id="标题">标题</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Level 1 Title</span><br><span class="line">## Level 2 Title</span><br><span class="line">### Level 3 Title</span><br><span class="line">#### Level 4 Title</span><br><span class="line">##### Level 5 Title</span><br><span class="line">###### Level 6 Title</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="列表">列表</h3><p>无序列表</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- List Item 1</span><br><span class="line">- List Item 2</span><br><span class="line">- List Item 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* List Item 4</span><br><span class="line">* List Item 5</span><br><span class="line">* List Item 6</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">+ List Item 7</span><br><span class="line">+ List Item 8</span><br><span class="line">+ List Item 9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有序列表</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. List Item 1</span><br><span class="line">2. List Item 2</span><br><span class="line">3. List Item 3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片和超链接">图片和超链接</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![desc](url)</span><br><span class="line">[desc](url)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="引用块">引用块</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; This is a test content</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="代码">代码</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This is inline code `console.log(&#x27;Hello World&#x27;)`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">This is a block code</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```js</span><br><span class="line">function fn() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    console.log(&#x27;Hello World&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="文本强调">文本强调</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*This is a test content (Italic)*</span><br><span class="line">_This is a test content (Italics)_</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">**This is a test content (Bold)**</span><br><span class="line">__This is a test content (Bold)__</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">***This is a test content (Italic and Bold)***</span><br><span class="line">___This is a test content (Italic and Bold)___</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="分隔符">分隔符</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">___</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="表格">表格</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| A1 | A2 | A3 |</span><br><span class="line">| -- | -- | -- |</span><br><span class="line">| B1 | B2 | B3 |</span><br><span class="line">| C1 | C2 | C3 |</span><br><span class="line">| D1 | D2 | D3 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="扩展语法">扩展语法</h2><h3 id="Emoji-表情">Emoji 表情</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:fire:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>🔥</p><h3 id="Mermaid-流程图">Mermaid 流程图</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph TD</span><br><span class="line">  A--&gt;B</span><br><span class="line">  B--&gt;C</span><br><span class="line">  B--&gt;D</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code class="highlight mermaid">graph TD  A--&gt;B  B--&gt;C  B--&gt;D</code></pre><h3 id="Mermaid-图表">Mermaid 图表</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% mermaid %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">pie</span><br><span class="line">title Language</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Java&quot; : 30</span><br><span class="line">&quot;HTML&quot; : 10</span><br><span class="line">&quot;CSS&quot; : 20</span><br><span class="line">&quot;JavaScript&quot; : 40</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endmermaid %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="mermaid-wrap"><pre class="mermaid-src" hidden>  pietitle Language&quot;Java&quot; : 30&quot;HTML&quot; : 10&quot;CSS&quot; : 20&quot;JavaScript&quot; : 40  </pre></div><h3 id="标签外挂">标签外挂</h3><h4 id="Tabs">Tabs</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs example %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab One --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">This is a test content 1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab Two --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">This is a test content 2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab Three --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">This is a test content 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tabs"><div class="nav-tabs"><button type="button" class="tab active">One</button><button type="button" class="tab">Two</button><button type="button" class="tab">Three</button></div><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active"><p>This is a test content 1</p></div><div class="tab-item-content"><p>This is a test content 2</p></div><div class="tab-item-content"><p>This is a test content 3</p></div></div><div class="tab-to-top"><button type="button" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div><h4 id="Tag-hide">Tag-hide</h4><h5 id="inline">inline</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hide Content: &#123;% hideInline This is a test content, View %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Hide Content: <span class="hide-inline"><button type="button" class="hide-button" style=""> View  </button><span class="hide-content">This is a test content</span></span></p><h5 id="block">block</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hide Content</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% hideBlock View %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">This is a test content 1</span><br><span class="line">This is a test content 2</span><br><span class="line">This is a test content 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endhideBlock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Hide Content</p><div class="hide-block"><button type="button" class="hide-button" style="">View    </button><div class="hide-content"><p>This is a test content 1<br>This is a test content 2<br>This is a test content 3</p></div></div><h4 id="Timeline">Timeline</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% timeline 2019 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- timeline 08-07 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">This is a test content</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtimeline --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtimeline %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="timeline "><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2019</p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>08-07</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>This is a test content</p></div></div></div><h4 id="ChartJS-图表">ChartJS 图表</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% chartjs %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- chart --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;type&quot;: &quot;line&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;data&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;labels&quot;: [&quot;Monday&quot;, &quot;Tuesday&quot;, &quot;Wednesday&quot;, &quot;Thursday&quot;, &quot;Friday&quot;, &quot;Saturday&quot;, &quot;Sunday&quot;],</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;datasets&quot;: [&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Count&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">            &quot;backgroundColor&quot;: &quot;#d63384&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">            &quot;borderColor&quot;: &quot;#d63384&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">            &quot;data&quot;: [0, 10, 50, 20, 30, 60, 70]</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;]</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;options&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;responsive&quot;: true</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endchart --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endchartjs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="chartjs-container" data-chartjs-id="" >            <pre class="chartjs-src" hidden>{    &quot;type&quot;: &quot;line&quot;,    &quot;data&quot;: {        &quot;labels&quot;: [&quot;Monday&quot;, &quot;Tuesday&quot;, &quot;Wednesday&quot;, &quot;Thursday&quot;, &quot;Friday&quot;, &quot;Saturday&quot;, &quot;Sunday&quot;],        &quot;datasets&quot;: [{            &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Count&quot;,            &quot;backgroundColor&quot;: &quot;#d63384&quot;,            &quot;borderColor&quot;: &quot;#d63384&quot;,            &quot;data&quot;: [0, 10, 50, 20, 30, 60, 70]        }]    },    &quot;options&quot;: {        &quot;responsive&quot;: true    }}</pre>                      </div><h4 id="IFrame">IFrame</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% iframe /single/example/ %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="el-tag-iframe"><div class="el-dots"><span class="el-dot"></span><span class="el-dot"></span><span class="el-dot"></span></div><iframe src="/single/example/"></iframe></div><h4 id="Image">Image</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% img /media/other/markdown/0.png %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="el-tag-img"><img src="/media/other/markdown/0.png"></div><h4 id="Video">Video</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% video /media/other/markdown/0.mp4 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="el-tag-video"><video src="/media/other/markdown/0.mp4" controls></video></div>]]></content>
      
      
